%div.faq-container
  %h1 FAQ

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 What is Deal Docks?
    %p Deal Docks is an online marketplace where you can buy and sell a wide variety of items.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 How do I create an account?
    %p You can create an account by clicking the 'Sign Up' button on the homepage and filling in the required information.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 How do I list an item for sale?
    %p After logging in, click on the 'Sell' button and fill out the form with your item's details.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 What payment methods are accepted?
    %p We accept various payment methods including credit cards and PayPal.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 How can I contact a seller?
    %p You can contact a seller through the messaging feature on their item's page.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 What should I do if I have a problem with a purchase?
    %p Please contact our customer support team for assistance with any purchase issues.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 Is my personal information secure?
    %p Yes, we take data security very seriously and use various measures to protect your personal information.

  %div.faq-item
    %h2 How can I delete my account?
    %p If you wish to delete your account, please contact our customer support team for assistance.

